         !text "            Mission: Asteroid           "
         !text "        (c) 1980 On-Line Systems        "
         !text "                                        "
         !text "by. . . . . . . . . . . . . Ken Williams"
         !text "  . . . . . . . . . . . Roberta Williams"
         !text "                                        "
         !text "In this adventure you find that an      "
         !text "asteroid is about to hit the Earth and  "
         !text "destroy it. It is your mission, as an   "
         !text "astronaut, to rocket to the asteroid and"
         !text "blow it up before it reaches Earth.     "
         !text "                                        "
         !text "You must fight through the red tape at  "
         !text "Mission Control, then enter the rocket  "
         !text "ship and learn how to fly it. I hope you"
         !text "find your way through space to the      "
         !text "asteroid.                               "
         !text "                                        "
         !text "Be careful with the explosives, as they "
         !text "can be very dangerous if not handled    "
         !text "correctly.                              "
         !text "                                        "
